data.description: Welcome to this captivating home nestled on a private lot, offering tranquility and modern living. As you drive up you will notice immediately the updated landscaping, new driveway, roof, decking and cable railing. Step inside and be greeted by an updated kitchen boasting new appliances and cabinets. The main bath showcases new cabinet with double sinks, while the lower bath is a true oasis with impeccable new tiled shower. You will notice new flooring throughout the home and beautiful staircase which features cable railing. The garage has been insulated. Relax and entertain on either the front or back deck. The upper back yard offers plenty of space for a firepit, playground, or for outdoor games.
